Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.29,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.29,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.45,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:58.00,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:05.01,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.15,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:22.50,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.50,0:01:27.23,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:34.17,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to miss my train!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko is late!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Tomoko was early today, because of her club meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.73,0:02:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me yesterday that she'd be going early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have not been myself lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that basketball practice game,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've had no peace of mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,With life overflowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So radiant... Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She was utterly sublime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there is Shinobu Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...openly displaying her fiery love for Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.89,0:03:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...her love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,18. Into the Dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Next stop is Seiran School.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.21,0:04:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps one should just "let it go its own way" ...as they say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your morning classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... biology, French, ...and P.E.!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of your French...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So come along with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the two sugars,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As shown on the board, depending on which sugar is present,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...DNA - deoxyribonucleic acid and RNA - Ribonucleic Acid, are separated out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You... you're really skipping class?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm coming. I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine it, Dear Brother. I'm skipping class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting my bag in the coin locker, and playing hooky...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I'm really doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can hardly believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:52.14,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,C'etait un jeune homme et une jeune femme
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:56.40,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,dans la mise se recherche, nous paru tres propre...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like everyone's watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...here I am, walking with Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get sandwiches... and a couple of boiled eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Be back in a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... I'm sorry. It's just for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A truant officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you in school? You're a student, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Which school? Is it near here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see your school I.D. please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't show it to me? In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind your school's name, then. Just name and address.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I'll need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She do something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's with me today. Today is Founder's Day at the schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to see the Big City.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Big City"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a country girl. From where all the wild pigs live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.61,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I brought her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it, then. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy yourselves. But be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a man with you, though, it should be all right. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be really convenient, everyone mistaking me for an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...but she thought I was a man, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.26,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared to death! Really! I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Nanako took today off after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like a butterfly who's lost one of her wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come to our basketball practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'll be there! For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inviting Rei, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To skip your classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't say that, call it a "self-proclaimed" vacation instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Self-proclaimed"? Yes, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't very nice, what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...calling me a country girl, from the land of wild pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be grateful it was "pigs" instead of "bears and wolves"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, look at this! They managed to get here after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes my punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What bad timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...to run into my Brother now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's with that same guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.18,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We only meet by odd coincidences, I guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I guess so! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I mailed you the program for our school's fair this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'd like it if you could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Gakuin University?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way... what's happening today? Is school out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Rei! Rei took her out of school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Live however you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't get her involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.99,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Brother"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,"Brother"? Saint-Juste-sama's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Him? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you call him "brother"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That... was Ichinomiya Takashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya Takashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ichinomiya Takashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya? Is that right? From the Ichinomiya family?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's a friend of Henmi Takehiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ichinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Ichinomiya Fukiko's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the oldest son of the Ichinomiya family,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...and also... he is my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Saint-Juste-sama's brother? Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Ichinomiya Takashi... is Saint-Juste-sama's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw him last at Saint-Juste-sama's apartment building...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have been visiting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no... my friend is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't he just tell me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichinomiya Takashi... Ichinomiya Fukiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Saint-Juste-sama's name is Asaka Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.53,0:14:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they aren't the usual sisters and brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Saint-Juste-sama has a different mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why are you looking so serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that. Eat your sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you eat the potato salad sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.56,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone bad! It's turned sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? How's your stomach? What can we do!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The value of a human life is no more than of an ant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it matters little if an ant dies...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.64,0:15:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san, are you alone? Where's Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know, Tomoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.92,0:15:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not on the absent list. Maybe she has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows. Anyway let's go sit down and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'm eating with Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, indeed you are, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's out today? I'll stop by her place after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle introduced me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle introduced me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.48,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh look, it's Orihara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That game was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your injury okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck next game!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone saw her on the bus. But she didn't show up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.59,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been set free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably just didn't feel like coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning, she and I spent hours together, alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Long, quiet, peaceful hours... walking around the pond,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...surrounded by flowers, listening to the birds singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama was in her own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Standing by her, I found myself gazing into her world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it was a world I couldn't enter myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...I could see in. I alone, and no one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,During a moment in time which lasted forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...I looked in with nothing to block my view. I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ma cherie La Poupee"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"My dear sweet doll"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She said that, repeatedly, while looking at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A doll to be loved on a whim, then forgotten on a whim?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But what does that make me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I to Saint-Juste-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Those answers are ones I must find within myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now, I will just enjoy living this moment in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute, one second, bathed in this radiant light,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...hearing the breezes like music in my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let me never awaken from this dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful case!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an ashtray case?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a present. From a freshman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, she wants my cigarette butts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll smoke them later, she said. Bad girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I did the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, give me that cigarette!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.11,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'll smoke it. I can smoke too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.02,0:19:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop pretending. You can't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.45,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can! Yes, I can smoke, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.66,0:19:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok then. I'll show you how to smoke. The real way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama! What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it! Inhale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Inhale deeply! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Her smiling lips, her hair like threads of silk...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.75,0:22:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she an angel ...or the devil!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't smoke. It doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you staying just as you are... until the end of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart trusts in her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...this woman of tenderness and gentle words.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.75,0:23:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't the will to think this is just a devil's sweet talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.31,0:23:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.10,0:23:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.81,0:24:14.01,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:19.48,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.95,0:24:25.09,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.09,0:24:30.56,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.30,0:24:36.84,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.84,0:24:42.31,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.31,0:24:45.04,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.04,0:24:47.85,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.85,0:24:50.25,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.25,0:24:55.52,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.04,0:25:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako can only guess what Saint-Juste feels for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.69,0:25:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensing Nanako's anxiety, Kaoru confides in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.49,0:25:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Nanako discovers Kaoru-no-Kimi's secret past....
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.67,0:25:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: The Utakata Game
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.21,0:25:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
